  "2026-07-02T15:11:16.507Z",claude-code-agent,"Investigation note: duplicate-safe all-status search found canonical CodeFactor epic pm-92if and closed category children pm-arzz/pm-fmjy/pm-0n6p/pm-g7vl/pm-zro7/pm-lzzp; no active child covered the fresh 2026-07-02 CodeFactor main snapshot. Public CodeFactor currently reports 27 active issues: 16 complexity and 11 duplication. GitHub sweep found no open PRs, no open issues, and no open Dependabot/code-scanning/secret-scanning alerts."
  "2026-07-02T15:50:28.169Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: refactored residual CodeFactor complexity hotspots across 15 production files plus focused branch coverage in health/error-guidance tests. Live CodeFactor snapshot at start was 27 issues on main; local stricter ESLint complexity(max=15) probe reduced from 65 to 48 findings. Verification passed: pm test pm-bssk --run --progress (git diff --check, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage at 100/100/100/100, focused create/health/init/next/profile/cli-main/sdk tests, pnpm lint with 0 jscpd clones, pnpm quality:static, pnpm typecheck). Manual packed install smoke passed in a fresh temp project using pnpm pack + npm install tarball: pm init --defaults --json, pm create --json, pm list --format json, pm search --status all, pm health --check-only --summary --json, pm validate --check-history-drift --json."
  "2026-07-02T16:13:53.589Z",claude-code-agent,"Review follow-up: applied CodeRabbit feedback for the health storage summarizer comment, deduplicated error-context and dynamic extension option-name normalization helpers, and switched canonical serialization key ordering to default code-unit sort. Verification: focused affected tests passed (5 files, 308 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, pnpm lint passed, and full coverage passed at 262 files / 5277 tests with 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines."
  "2026-07-02T16:19:49.189Z",claude-code-agent,"Review follow-up update: addressed local Greptile findings before push by removing the one-call dynamicExtensionOptionNames wrapper, dropping the redundant help-json examples cast, and documenting locale-independent canonical serialization key ordering. Verification: targeted help/extension/serialization tests passed (4 files, 234 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, and pnpm lint passed with 0 jscpd clones and static quality clean."
